, with accounts that span sociological, cultural, and economic forms of analysis.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Mai 2023) 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh1 aAdkins, Lisa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBjerg, Ole, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBowsher, Joshua, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aCartwright, Laura, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDavis, Mark, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDawney, Leila, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDeville, Joe, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFeatherstone, Mark, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFeatherstone, Mark, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aGane, Nicholas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHaiven, Max, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKirwan, Samuel, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWalker, Rosie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z97831111966880 cprintz978144733954040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781447339533423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781447339533/original  a978-3-11-119668-8  Bristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  aGBV-deGruyter-alles